paragraph.value: Results on the MSRA dataset are shown in Table 6.  Our chosen segmentor gives 95.93% accuracy on 5-fold cross-validated training set.  Compared with the existing methods, our wordbased and character-based LSTM-CRF models give competitive accuracies. The lattice model significantly outperforms both the best characterbased and word-based models (p < 0.01), achieving the best result on this standard benchmark.
